thread.title: Flynn the bichon frise fetches top prize at dog show

title: Flynn the bichon frise fetches top prize at dog show
text:
Flynn the bichon frise fetches top prize at dog show 9:43pm IST - 00:36 
A bichon frise named Flynn was crowned ''best in show'' at the 142nd Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show on Tuesday, wagging his tail to triumph over nearly 3,000 dogs entered in the world-renowned contest for pure-bred canines. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
